high_descs: Move forward to the round dining table.
Pick up the potato on the table.
Turn left, bring the potato to the microwave.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
Take the heated potato from the microwave, turn around, bring the potato to the fridge.
Put the heated potato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Walk forward and go to the table on your left.
Pick up the potato from the table.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Heat the potato and pick it up again.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Put the potato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Pick up the potato near the spatula on the table.
Turn right and head towards the microwave on the counter.
Place the potato in the microwave, heat it up, and take it back out.
Turn right towards the sink and then turn right towards the fridge.
Place the potato on the top right shelf inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked potato on the top right shelf inside the fridge.
